snippet.title: eBaseball Pro Yakyuu Spirits 2021: Grand Slam (Switch) - Gameplay
snippet.description:
A full game of Konami's Pro Yakyuu Spirits 2021 for the Nintendo Switch. Yakult Swallows at Orix Buffaloes. 

If you follow MLB, look out for Adam Jones on the Orix Buffaloes, and former Pirate Jose Osuna and former Brewer Domingo Santana on the Yakult Swallows.
